Package: bojstat
Title: R Interface to the Bank of Japan Time-Series Data Search API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kazuki", "Hosoda", email = "placeholder@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to access the Bank of Japan (BOJ) Time-Series 
    Data Search API, which was launched on February 18, 2026. Users can retrieve 
    over 200,000 time-series statistical data in JSON or CSV format, including 
    interest rates, exchange rates, money stock, Tankan survey results, price 
    indices, and more. The package supports the three API types provided by BOJ: 
    the Code API (retrieve data by series code), the Layer API (retrieve data by 
    hierarchical structure), and the Metadata API (retrieve series metadata).
